seq_len:  1024

```

<!-- livebook:{"output":true} -->

```
:ok
```

## Run benchmarks

```elixir
results =
  checkpoints
  |> Enum.reject(& &1.skip?)
  |> Enum.shuffle()
  |> Enum.map(fn checkpoint ->
    try do
      {:ok, Runner.run_checkpoint(checkpoint, cfg)}
    rescue
      exception -> {:error, checkpoint.label, Exception.format(:error, exception, __STACKTRACE__)}
    end
  end)

:ok
```

